{"id":330548,"type":1,"name":"王都妖奇譚","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/87/2a/330548_ddhjm.jpg","summary":"      《王都妖奇谭》是岩崎阳子创作的漫画，主要讲述了安倍晴明与好友藤原将之联手对抗师兄橘影连的京都保卫战。同为阴阳寮下学习的安倍晴明与橘影连走上了不同的道路，晴明拒绝了影连的鼓动，后者为报灭门之恨发誓要毁灭京城。期间，安倍晴明更因遇见了右大臣的少子、当今皇上宠妃的兄弟——藤原将之，从相互嫌弃到结下深厚友谊，发生了一系列紧张有趣的故事。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>王都妖奇谭</li><li><span>册数: </span>12</li><li><span>话数: </span>32</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/41257\">岩崎陽子</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/7571\">秋田書店</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/11814\">プリンセスGOLD</a></li><li><span>连载开始: </span>1990年</li><li><span>连载结束: </span>2002年</li>","staff":[{"id":41257,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7a/88/41257_prsn_6lUlc.jpg","name":"岩崎阳子","desc":"作者"},{"id":7571,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/28/b1/7571_prsn_vckUV.jpg","name":"秋田书店","desc":"出版社"},{"id":11814,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/59/e6/11814_prsn_YE8xM.jpg","name":"プリンセスGOLD","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":330547,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/b5/fd/330547_fC3jQ.jpg"},{"id":330550,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/4d/b3/330550_8sQvr.jpg"},{"id":330551,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/43/de/330551_BOse7.jpg"},{"id":330552,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/7b/ed/330552_1Q39f.jpg"},{"id":330553,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9b/29/330553_1x73V.jpg"},{"id":330556,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/fd/ca/330556_4cOFq.jpg"},{"id":330557,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/21/10/330557_7b987.jpg"},{"id":330558,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/73/8d/330558_ho55z.jpg"},{"id":330559,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (9)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/33/49/330559_EPH7i.jpg"},{"id":330560,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (10)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/31/1d/330560_v2V90.jpg"},{"id":330561,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (11)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/10/65/330561_62Y27.jpg"},{"id":330562,"name":"王都妖奇譚 (12